      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the syndrome thing but he's actually feeling really rough right now and the ibuprofen i have is expired. i just need to know if a little bit of aspirin would work to get him through the night until we can call the doctor in the morning? i just want to make sure it's actually effective for a fever his age.",
